Perfume rating 4.25 out of 5 with 284 votes
Mazaaj Infused by Zimaya is a Citrus Aromatic fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Mazaaj Infused was launched in 2024. Top notes are Citron, Bergamot and Orange; middle notes are Ginger and Neroli; base notes are Ambroxan, Olibanum and Woody Notes. 
Mazaaj Infused pour homme by Zimaya captures the senses and transports the wearer to realms of imagination and inspiration. This unique blend is an invitation to embrace the magic of the imagination and embark on a voyage of discovery and delight.
